    <br />
    <b>Reminder:</b> Services referred by APS should be updated in the Client Status form throughout the case.
    <br />
    Caseworkers should review and consider this summary at each 90-day review and at closure.
    <br />
    Reflect on progress in the case, changed circumstances and newly identified needs.
    <br />
    Have appropriate services been offered based on known risks? Have services been offered based on known client goals? Have all referrals for services been made and followed through on?
    <br />

</div>

